@startuml Use Case - Voice Translation
title Use Case: Voice & Text Translation

left to right direction

actor "User" as User
actor "Translation API" as API
actor "Expo Speech (TTS)" as TTS
actor "Supabase (DB)" as DB

rectangle "Translation Screen" {
    usecase "Enter Text Manually" as UC_InputText
    usecase "Speak to Translate (STT)" as UC_InputVoice
    usecase "Select Languages" as UC_SelectLang
    usecase "View Translation" as UC_View
    usecase "Play Audio (TTS)" as UC_Play
    usecase "Copy to Clipboard" as UC_Copy
    usecase "Auto-Save to History" as UC_Save
}

User --> UC_InputText
User --> UC_InputVoice
User --> UC_SelectLang
User --> UC_Play
User --> UC_Copy

UC_InputVoice ..> UC_View : leads to
UC_InputText ..> UC_View : leads to

UC_View ..> API : detect & translate
UC_Play ..> TTS : speak text

UC_View ..> UC_Save : <<include>> (if logged in)
UC_Save ..> DB : insert record

@enduml